{"title":"红色的泉","authors":["严阵"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严阵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的山坡下面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一道清清的山泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉水从岩石中涌出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过绿绿的草原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在岩石的斜坡上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横刻着几个大字："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红色的泉”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒影在岩下的水潭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么叫它红色的泉啊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远路的旅人请不必多问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧羊女的歌声里可以找到回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不就请听响遍草原的马头琴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传说在十几年以前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里并没有泉水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有在人们的梦中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才看到它的银辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那块高大的岩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没有一丝裂缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原上巡飞的老鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常站在它的岩顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个冬天的夜里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风雪把天地弥漫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个勇敢的游击队员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战死在那块岩石下面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二天黎明时分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个老人从岩下经过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见从那血染的岩石上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆裂出一道清波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉水喷着银花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过冰封的草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄了的草又绿了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖上又落满大雁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人望着泉水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔出银色的短剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为刻下泉水的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他攀上高高的石岩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉水日夜流着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过艰苦的年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它就像一条血管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔流着伟大的爱。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}